1428
01:05:33,820 --> 01:05:35,820
2j plus 1 is 3 states.

1429
01:05:35,820 --> 01:05:37,820
And so forth and so on,

1430
01:05:37,820 --> 01:05:39,820
depending on the spin of the particle.

1431
01:05:39,820 --> 01:05:43,820
Now, a photon only has 2 spin states.

1432
01:05:43,820 --> 01:05:47,820
And that's connected with the fact that it's massless.

1433
01:05:47,820 --> 01:05:49,820
So, let's say some things about

