1475
01:07:19,820 --> 01:07:21,820
All right, so we brought it to rest,

1476
01:07:21,820 --> 01:07:23,820
and now we're going to run along its direction.

1477
01:07:23,820 --> 01:07:25,820
All right, so we brought it to rest,

1478
01:07:25,820 --> 01:07:28,820
and then transformed it in some other direction.

1479
01:07:28,820 --> 01:07:31,820
So therefore, if a photon is massive,

1480
01:07:31,820 --> 01:07:35,820
