1481
01:07:35,820 --> 01:07:37,820
It has to have spin along its axis,

1482
01:07:37,820 --> 01:07:39,820
spin opposite to its axis,

1483
01:07:39,820 --> 01:07:44,820
and the third spin state also.

1484
01:07:44,820 --> 01:07:46,820
On the other hand,

1485
01:07:46,820 --> 01:07:49,820
if the photon is massive, massless,

1486
01:07:49,820 --> 01:07:51,820
you can't bring it to rest.

1487
01:07:51,820 --> 01:07:52,820
You can't bring it to rest.

1488
01:07:52,820 --> 01:07:53,820
You can't do this opposite thing.

1489
01:07:53,820 --> 01:07:55,820
You can't do this opposite operation.

1490
01:07:55,820 --> 01:07:57,320
All you can do is rotate

1491
01:07:57,320 --> 01:07:58,820
